<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">Personally depending on the situation I go with wis and mana gear.  If its a raid I go with resist gear.  I always try to do the best I can with ac, however I choose the wis/mana/resists bonus over the ac bonus.<BR>To each his own though.  Do whatever you think works best for you.  Some play styles are a bit different than others and some feel more comfortable when they use a different tactic.  Not to say any are wrong.  Just different.</FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#f7f5e6"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=175"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of Llewyn"></a>
